text: Zareen Khan, birthly spelled as Zarine Khan, is an Indian actress and model who mainly working in the Hindi language movies. She has also appeared in Tamil, Telugu and Punjabi films. She made her debut in playing the role of a princess in 2010 war action drama film Veer. == References == Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Mumbai Category:Indian movie actors Category:Indian models
